#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:50
msgid ""
"This time it is the Object Data that is enclosed in the bounding box. The"
" bounding box in *Edit Mode* takes no account of the Object(s) origins, "
"only the center of the selected vertices."
msgstr ""

